"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Regarding the metaverse, there is a misunderstanding. People who are successful in the real world think from their standpoint and they need to establish a digital identity and map the real world to the virtual world. However, many gamers do not live well in the real world, and they need to feel accomplished in the game. They want to hide behind an idealized superego, instead of mapping reality to the virtual world. \\n\\nSuccessful people certainly want to continue their success in the real world to the virtual world. Imagine a picture: a successful 40-year-old businessman is beaten up by a primary school student in a game, how would he feel?\",\"timestamp\":1641139971,\"title\":\"Capsule（25.5.2021）Avatars in Metaverse\"},\"digest\":\"3Y9yNyD3zGY3jKP3VHvFTMo4Wqqh_yVYOnvUGvvhXFE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Q_daSr_Ip7HTHpknzoPqkP39ToJwqwC0LUz4QN_RNbeixrvhR3cJRMVzwWZb7Hnj8o2YMS-4t23m_Zzmd0eQvw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x24845bd906a3dcd3a6a2c8def0e1867a94aa37e04d35018a13b94099ae5be24d4b1abdd27984d765963fd65aa852fe7e1dc6d3934335a6e14328e5bca1565db21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"3Y9yNyD3zGY3jKP3VHvFTMo4Wqqh_yVYOnvUGvvhXFE\"}"